text.section:
The General Assembly declares that:
It is State public policy to both restore existing park and green space systems and create new park and green space systems in the municipal corporations of the State and Baltimore City; and
Funding sources in the form of flexible grants shall be made available to the governing bodies of municipal corporations and Baltimore City to:
Rehabilitate, expand, improve, or maintain existing parks;
Purchase land to create new parks;
Develop new parks;
Purchase and install playground equipment in urban neighborhoods and rural areas throughout the State; or
Be used for environmentally oriented parks and recreation projects.
